   <body>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCe236b8682b27100586e1b8b5655f9dd2"></a>Refitting the clutch master cylinder assembly
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6466"> </a>Fit the clutch master cylinder assembly (3) to left side handlebar, inserting centring pin (A) on handlebar into hole (B)
            on clutch master cylinder control.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_018203277.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6471"> </a>Match clamp (6) to clutch master cylinder control and fasten them using screws (5).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6473"> </a>Tighten fixing screws (5) to a torque of 10 Nm ±10%, following a 1-2-1 sequence starting from the upper screw.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_039503860.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6478"> </a>Locate the hose (4) and sealing washers (2) on the master cylinder unit (3) and secure with the special screw (1), without
            tightening.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/warning.jpg">Warning
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6481"> </a>An incorrectly positioned hose can cause clutch faults and interfere with moving parts.
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6484"> </a>To position clutch line (4) and hose clamps, refer to "<a href="78740.html#DUC1fe52c982b2410058cedd30e2bfae6c4">Refitting the clutch slave cylinder</a>".
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6489"> </a>Tighten the special screw (1) to a torque of 23 Nm ±10%.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_017903274.jpg"></center>
      </div>
